ItemSlider v1.0

Description
This jQuery plugin provides a basic, ultra lightweight carousel,
which is also very flexible, as it allows any type of content to be used.

Usage
1. Include jQuery and the .css and .js files of the project.
2. Run the following method on the jQuery object:

$('#item_container').itemslider();

For further details, please consult the example.html file.

Options

1. items_limit: how many items to be shown at the same time (default: 8)
2. fade_time: the fade in time of appearing items (default: 300ms)

CSS Classes

You can modify the items' style, as well as the left and right buttons.



